  "id": "RAW_2cf079",
  "title": "字节 Dreamina 斩获头名，4 款华人产品进入前十！ Product Hunt 精选 37",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6xmBCm1VkZWeQaKW9S4AOw",
  "date": "2025-02-23 07:11:50",
  "author": "若曦 Ross",
  "siteName": "随机小分队",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\">\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\">\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Product Hunt是全球最流行的发掘有意思新产品的平台。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">经过近十年的发展，已经成为用户发现新产品、创业者获得灵感、投资人寻找新机会，以及创始人对产品进行推广的最好地方。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025 年的第一期月榜中，华人团队大放异彩，有四款产品进入前十，字节跳动的两款 AI 产品 Dreamina 和 Trae 分列第一和第七；此外去年曾勇夺五月月榜第一的 AI 建站工具 Wegic 和虚拟人视频新秀 JoggAI 也都取得了不错的成绩。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">话不多说，下面就请来具体看看本期有趣的产品。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h8s79jhs3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h8s79vrm4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">1.D</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h8s79jhs3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h8s79vrm4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">reamina：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h8s79jhs3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h8s79vrm4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">字节的文生图工具</span></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">字节的 AI 文生图工具 Dreamina（即梦海外版）在 2025 年的第一期月榜中勇夺头名，为华人团队开了个好头。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dreamina 适用于多种创意场景，除了文生图外，还支持对图像进行高精度编辑，如擦除、重绘、清晰度增强等。此外，Dreamina 也包含视频生成能力，并支持对运镜、时长、视频比例等进行自定义。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6de41261-7e10-4612-753a-8d5bffc0d700/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"735\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100019728\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6de41261-7e10-4612-753a-8d5bffc0d700/public\"></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dreamina 提供免费版本，包含 120 个 Credits(每张图片消耗 2 个)，付费版定价为 15-70 美元/月，提供更多 Credits。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1528</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：dreamina.capcut.com</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: center;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">2.Wegic：AI 网站搭建工具</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">恭喜 Wegic 团队在去年五月斩获月榜榜一后，又在今年一月月榜中获得了第二名的好成绩！我们在曾在“</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTAwMzU1MA==&amp;mid=2247492573&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5e55528c45fd3368bfad975ed54e4921&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"月榜冠军 Wegic 独家专访，又一个中国团队首秀登顶的复盘！\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">月榜冠军 Wegic 独家专访，又一个中国团队首秀登顶的复盘！</span></a></span></span><span leaf=\"\">”一文中对 Wegic 团队进行过深度专访。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">网站建设和管理通常需要设计、开发和维护等多环节协作，技术门槛高、时间成本大。Wegic 通过 AI 整合了设计、开发和管理的能力，大幅简化了网站从创建到运营的全过程。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Wegic 适用于企业官网、个人作品集和在线服务等场景，其最大特点是可以完全通过 AI 构建和管理一整个网站，用户不需要有任何基础即可通过 Prompt 实现所有功能，创建非常美观的网站。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2554e849-27b0-4b08-8d99-853a196fc100/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"735\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100019725\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2554e849-27b0-4b08-8d99-853a196fc100/public\"></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Wegic 提供免费版本，支持 1 个网站和少量 Credits；付费版定价为 11.9-19.9 美元/月，支持自定义域名、无限页面、Google Analytics 集成等功能。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1448</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：wegic.ai</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h8v4hwn07\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h8v4i8rhy\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">3.Sagehood：用于美股分析的 Agent</span></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资者在股票市场中常面临信息过载、工具分散、决策复杂等问题，导致效率低下且容易出错。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sagehood 适用于希望优化投资策略的美股投资者，其核心功能包括：预开盘预测（提供每日市场趋势和风险分析）、个性化股票推荐（根据用户财务目标和风险偏好定制）、360°投资组合监控（实时跟踪投资动态）。此外，Sagehood 还提供新闻分析、社交媒体情绪追踪、风险管理和技术交易建议等，显著提升投资效率。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a7178b9d-7be5-4ab1-e677-97d0a8dbd100/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"735\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100019724\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a7178b9d-7be5-4ab1-e677-97d0a8dbd100/public\"></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sagehood 提供免费版本；付费版本尚未公开具体价格，包括深度市场分析和更高级的 AI 支持。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1404</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：sagehood.ai</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: center;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span data-token-index=\"1\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">4.TestSprite 1.0</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">：软件自动化测试 Agent</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">软件测试通常耗时费力，开发团队需要手动创建测试用例、编写测试代码、诊断问题并提出修复方案。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">TestSprite 适用于中早期团队，专注于提升测试效率和覆盖率，让开发者能够专注于产品开发，而无需手动执行测试流程。其核心功能包括：AI 自动生成测试用例、自动化测试代码编写、后端 API 测试、前端界面测试、 通过自然语言调整测试用例等。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d16684fd-4c14-42ec-2f73-9f37f22cbe00/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.561941251596424\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"783\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100019726\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d16684fd-4c14-42ec-2f73-9f37f22cbe00/public\"></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">TestSprite 提供免费社区版本，支持基本测试功能；付费版本包含 AI 驱动的根因分析、前端测试可视化报告等高级功能，目前尚未公布价格。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1323</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：testsprite.com</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: center;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h93b7o444\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h93b82um7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">5.21st.dev：UI 组件库</span></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h93lux7v5\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h93lvaetj\"><br></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端开发者在构建专业、美观的网站时，常面临设计资源匮乏、重复开发 UI 组件以及缺乏灵感等问题。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">21st.dev 适用于需要快速构建网站的用户，特别是从事 AI 应用开发的团队。平台核心功能包括：大量 UI 组件，支持直接复制代码粘贴至 v0、Cursor、Bolt、Lovable、Replit 等工具；汇集 50 多位专业设计工程师的作品；还提供社区供大家交流与分享。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/45a16be4-5c91-4cac-bbc6-a45009d50200/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5314009661835749\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"border-radius: 0px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"100019727\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/45a16be4-5c91-4cac-bbc6-a45009d50200/public\"></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">21st.dev 目前完全免费，他们还推出了一款可以用于生成 UI 元素的 AI Agent——Magic，目前仍在 Waitlist，这款产品定价为 10-30 美元/月。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：1344</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：21st.dev</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;marg