, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h95ik0lnr\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h95ikb1slc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">7.Trae：AI 编程工具</span></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">字节的产品再次登榜！其 AI 编程工具 Trae 获得了一月月榜第七名。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Trae 主要服务于开发者和技术团队，适用于代码编写、任务规划和跨团队协作等场景。其核心功能包括：实时 AI 编程助手，可理解整个代码库并提供智能建议；自动任务分解和执行，简化开发工作流；上下文感知的智能补全功能，超越传统的自动补全；多模态 AI 支持，能够精准处理和理解视觉内容。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n       <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23ed3f16-98e7-4d7d-c10d-f6bbee7b6a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100019730\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23ed3f16-98e7-4d7d-c10d-f6bbee7b6a00/public\">\n      </section>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Trae 提供了 Windows 和 Mac 版本，目前完全免费。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：980</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：trae.ai</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h960m41o45\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h960mh20t0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">8.Raycast Focus：应用和网站屏蔽工具</span></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">各种 APP、网站的诱惑太多，让很多人在工作和学习中经常分散注意力导致效率下降。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raycast Focus 是 Mac 知名工具 Raycast 的又一个小产品，主要帮助用户更加专注，其核心功能包括：设定专注目标、选择专注时长、设定屏蔽的应用和网站。此外，Raycast Focus 也支持用户灵活控制，在必要时暂停屏蔽功能，处理完紧急事务后还可快速回归专注状态。</span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n      </figure>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n      <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8ca3743e-571c-4fc4-ff29-55f4928c6900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100019729\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8ca3743e-571c-4fc4-ff29-55f4928c6900/public\">\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raycast Free 和 Pro 版本中都包含了 Raycast Focus 的功能。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：926</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：raycast.com</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h97xb812yn\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h97xbl1xmg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">9.Builder.io with Lovable：Figma 设计转 APP 工具</span></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在传统的设计与开发流程中，设计师与工程师之间的协作效率低下、手动将设计转化为代码耗时且容易出错。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Builder.io 带来了与知名无代码应用构建工具 Lovable 的集成，支持从原型开发到生产级应用的全流程。其核心功能包括：在 Figma 设计后直接通过Builder.io</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;插件导出代码、无缝对接 Lovable 平台进行应用开发、并支持用户通过 Prompt 进一步优化代码。此外，Builder.io 还提供了设计与代码双向同步的能力，用户在 Figma 中更新设计后可直接推送到应用中，确保设计与开发一致性。</span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n      </figure>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n      <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/651b750e-1cf6-48ad-989b-a5e1aacb2000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100019733\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/651b750e-1cf6-48ad-989b-a5e1aacb2000/public\">\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Builder.io 的免费版本提供了较少的用量，付费版定价为 24 美元/月。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：931</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验地址：builder.io</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m7h9ayb51s75\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m7h9aybkdv8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">10.AI Follow-ups by folk：AI 销售线索管理工具</span></span>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统 CRM 需要大量手动操作，如更新联系人信息、筛选潜在客户和撰写跟进邮件，导致销售团队浪费很多时间在这些基础工作。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI Follow-ups by folk 适用于服务型企业和销售团队，尤其是希望提升客户管理效率的中小型团队。其核心功能包括：通过 AI 分析历史对话、识别最佳跟进对象，生成个性化回复建议，与邮件、日历和社交媒体集成来实现数据同步与管理。此外，folk 还提供高度可定制的 CRM 界面，可自由配置邮件序列、仪表盘、交易管理等功能。</span></p>\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n      </figure>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n      <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ee96ff62-a228-400d-41fc-6322e8878a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5986394557823129\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100019732\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ee96ff62-a228-400d-41fc-6322e8878a00/public\">\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n      <figure style=\"margin: 0;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n      </figure>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">folk 提供免费试用，付费版定价为 20-80 美元/月，提供更多用量及专属支持服务。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点赞数：837</span></p>\n      <p style=\"paddi